NEXT_PUBLIC_LOCALES=en,es,fr,de,hi,ta,te,kn,ml,ha,yo,ig,ff,sw,ki,lu,lo,am,om,ti,so,lg,nyn,ach,ak,ee,gaa,dag,zu,xh,af,nso,tn,st,ts,ss,ve,nr,ar,nu

